flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Backup Type}
    B -->|Cloud| C[Perform Cloud Backup]
    B -->|Local| D[Perform Local Backup]
    C --> E[Backup Complete]
    D --> E
    E --> F{Restore Type}
    F -->|Cloud| G[Restore from Cloud]
    F -->|Local| H[Restore from Local]
    G --> I[Restore Complete]
    H --> I
    I --> J{Sync Type}
    J -->|Cross-Device| K[Sync Data Across Devices]
    J -->|Single Device| L[No Sync Required]
    K --> M[Sync Complete]
    L --> M
    M --> N[End]